br>		きのう買った<span class="style2">ケーキ</span>を食べましょう。　(Let's eat <font color="#0000FF">the		cake</font> I        bought yesterday.)                <br>      </p></td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td height="37" colspan="3"><img src="../../../../images/ｇvideo.jpg" alt="video icon" width="22" height="16" border="0"> <span class="style1">Example:</span> <a href="../../../gvideo/Relative Clauses.mov" target="_blank">movie          &quot;ご家族のパーティー&quot;</a></td>  </tr></table><p>&nbsp;</p><UL>	<LI>			<B>練習 (Practice Quizzes)</B><BR>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <p align="center"><a href="#top">Return to Top</a> </p> 			<p align="center"><a href="../../../../glist.php">Ｒeturn to Grammar Lists</a></p>	  </UL>          </tr></table></BODY></HTML>